results
Type: array object[]

A list of results. It can be empty if no results are found.

    accessibility
    Type: stringenum
    required

    Indicates whether this result is wheelchair accessible. The possible values are:
        None: not accessible
        WheelchairStrict: entirely accessible
        WheelchairTripsWithUnknownStops: The selected trip routes/vehicles are wheelchair accessible, but some stops used in the trip have unknown wheelchair accessibility status.
    values
        WheelchairStrict
        None
        WheelchairTripsWithUnknownStops
    duration
    Type: integer
    required

    The expected duration of the trip, in seconds.
    end_time
    Type: integer
    required

    The expected start time in unix time
    start_time
    Type: integer
    required

    The expected start time in unix time
    fare
    Type: object

    Object representing the price to pay for the entire trip plan. In most cases, the high and low price should be the same but can be different in some microtransit and bikeshare plans. Can be null if the fare is unknown.
